    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and double VANOS to deliver a linear 333 hp with an 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed via a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and an M-Variable Differential Lock. This vehicle is in concours-level condition with documented preventative maintenance addressing critical E46 weak points: the rod bearings have been replaced, the VANOS system has been overhauled with Beisan components, and the rear subframe has been reinforced. The chassis remains taut with factory-spec bushings and dampening, providing the precise turn-in and feedback characteristic of the chassis's 50/50 weight distribution. Zero oxidation, original paint meter readings, and a pristine undercarriage confirm its status as a collector-quality specimen.",
      "price": 48500.0,
